{"tid":2389975,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英保釋終審聆訊結束 終審庭將擇日頒下判詞 黎智英現須繼續還押","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T13:56:38.000Z","uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3787fa024739799b13dcc8f39ad03ba56dbd93","tid":2389975,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:08:39.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被控勾結外國勢力和欺詐，早前遭終審法院暫時撤銷保釋，等候處理律政司提出的法律問題上訴，釐清國安法的保釋規定。案件今由五名國安法指定法官審理，代表黎智英的資深大狀黃繼明陳詞指，批出保釋的高院法官沒有將國安法第42條與一般保釋法例等同，且已考慮國安法第42條（2）。黃又指，若要證明被告會繼續危害國安，責任在於控方。終院五位法官聽罷陳詞，將擇日頒判詞，黎智英須繼續還柙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/EOU7D25DAZAFZK764SFMWFT6DM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FEOU7D25DAZAFZK764SFMWFT6DM%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G4V%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=c009d6ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FEOU7D25DAZAFZK764SFMWFT6DM%2F&h=21eaa046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/EOU7D25DAZAFZK764SFMWFT6DM/</a>"},{"pid":"34da851708f04a21662e7d521f7fc48775d75e74","tid":2389975,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續還押"},{"pid":"3ed93367bb125563659cf5a3e50e1708fbbdc95e","tid":2389975,"uid":37596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"擇日到開審<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fc72feb18524447502f282352022f229a2f451","tid":2389975,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5afd389483019ca9537659e45d3e482b3db4ca","tid":2389975,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:12:57.000Z","msg":"律政司一方提出兩個關鍵論點....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國安法第42(2)條下，法官需要考慮被告會否繼續干犯「危害國家安全行為」，<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">並不限於國安法或香港特區現有法律。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n對於律政司談到保釋法官考慮被告其他行為，包括《基本法》23條，一向較溫文的陳兆愷也罕有發火質疑詢問：「如果本身合法，為什麼法官要考慮呢？」<br />\n<br />\n周天行解釋，律政司理解保釋要考慮行為分三種，分別是國安法、本港法律，及「危害國家安全的行為」。陳兆愷說，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">如果是危害國家安全行為，豈非可能睡覺都會違反國家安全？<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n李官及司徒敬分別指出，國安法其他條文只針對已生效的法例，例如國安法第8條列明是執法及司法機關執行「本法和香港特別行政區現行法律」。李官說，明白國家安全重要，但將不是罪行行為套用，怎樣有助國家安全？<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37682/黎智英-港版國安法-終審法院-37682/【黎智英保釋案】律政司力銷國安法大曬-23條未立已適用-終院圍攻律政司演繹等同無保釋?fbclid=IwAR3SO2EmF7mjKR_mzce1rIdFWnvSBXEP8131FKlkm2b7_mZuZqmML-oB-Go\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F37682%2F%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1-%E6%B8%AF%E7%89%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E7%B5%82%E5%AF%A9%E6%B3%95%E9%99%A2-37682%2F%E3%80%90%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E6%A1%88%E3%80%91%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%8A%9B%E9%8A%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E5%A4%A7%E6%9B%AC-23%E6%A2%9D%E6%9C%AA%E7%AB%8B%E5%B7%B2%E9%81%A9%E7%94%A8-%E7%B5%82%E9%99%A2%E5%9C%8D%E6%94%BB%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%BC%94%E7%B9%B9%E7%AD%89%E5%90%8C%E7%84%A1%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3SO2EmF7mjKR_mzce1rIdFWnvSBXEP8131FKlkm2b7_mZuZqmML-oB-Go&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G4V%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=10543b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37682/黎智英-港版國安法-終審法院-37682/【黎智英保釋案】律政司力銷國安法大曬-23條未立已適用-終院圍攻律政司演繹等同無保釋?fbclid=IwAR3SO2EmF7mjKR_mzce1rIdFWnvSBXEP8131FKlkm2b7_mZuZqmML-oB-Go</a>"},{"pid":"e04f59f2e70fe712cfa911d79e8